  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Chittagong Landslide Cash Response</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This is a response to the landslide disaster in Bangladesh. We will be providing cash transfers to support families in need of food and shelter. We conducted a door to door visitation was made by our staff to identify and enlist the households for benefits.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We will be distributing checks which can be used to receive cash in local banks. We will be using a card with a seal and QR code to avoid falsification which allows for double checking with mobile scanning when distributing.</narrative>
  </description>
